ath d="m16.852 17.772-.383.924"></path><path d="m19.148 12.228.383-.923"></path><path d="m19.53 18.696-.382-.924"></path><path d="m20.772 13.852.924-.383"></path><path d="m20.772 16.148.924.383"></path><circle cx="18" cy="15" r="3"></circle><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg></div><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800">Junior Product Support Executive</h2></div><div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border"><div class="space-y-6 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed"><div><p>We&#x27;re seeking enthusiastic individuals who grew up with technology and are passionate about helping others succeed with it. If you&#x27;re someone who naturally becomes the &quot;go-to tech person&quot; among friends and family, enjoys explaining how things work, and gets satisfaction from solving puzzles—this role could be perfect for you.</p></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">What You&#x27;ll Do</h3><ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 ml-4"><li>Be the friendly voice that helps healthcare providers and their teams make the most of our platform</li><li>Investigate and resolve questions about product features through conversations, emails, and support tickets</li><li>Create helpful content—write support articles, record tutorial videos, and build guides that make complex features easy to understand</li><li>Work alongside our product and technical teams to understand customer needs and improve our platform</li><li>Learn the ins and outs of digital healthcare technology, including how clinics, hospitals, and healthcare providers use our tools</li></ul></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">What We&#x27;re Looking For</h3><p class="mb-3">You don&#x27;t need prior work experience, but you should have:</p><ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 ml-4"><li><strong>Digital fluency:</strong> You&#x27;re comfortable navigating apps (mobile and web), exploring new features without hesitation, and learning software quickly</li><li><strong>Communication skills:</strong> You can explain technical concepts in simple terms, both in writing and conversation. You enjoy teaching others and have patience when someone doesn&#x27;t understand something the first time</li><li><strong>Problem-solving mindset:</strong> When something doesn&#x27;t work, you enjoy figuring out why. You ask good questions and think through possibilities systematically</li><li><strong>Curiosity:</strong> You genuinely want to understand how things work and aren&#x27;t satisfied with surface-level knowledge</li><li><strong>Customer empathy:</strong> You care about making people&#x27;s experience better and take pride in helping them succeed</li><li><strong>Self-motivation:</strong> You don&#x27;t wait to be told what to do—you see what needs attention and take initiative</li><li><strong>Adaptability:</strong> You&#x27;re comfortable with change and can switch between different types of tasks throughout the day</li></ul></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">Skills That Will Help You Succeed</h3><ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 ml-4"><li>Comfortable creating and editing content (articles, documents, presentations)</li><li>Experience making videos or screen recordings (even casual ones for friends/social media)</li><li>Good attention to detail—you notice when something is off</li><li>Basic understanding of how databases, APIs, or web services work (not mandatory, but helpful)</li><li>Interest in healthcare, wellness, or making a social impact</li></ul></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">What You&#x27;ll Gain</h3><ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 ml-4"><li>Deep knowledge of B2B SaaS operations and healthcare technology</li><li>Hands-on experience with product support, customer success, and technical communication</li><li>Mentorship from experienced team members who will invest in your growth</li><li>Exposure to real-world problem-solving with a global user base</li><li>A foundation for growth into product management, customer success, or technical roles</li></ul></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">Why ContinuousCare?</h3><p class="mb-4">You&#x27;ll work at the intersection of healthcare and technology, supporting a platform that genuinely improves patient care and healthcare delivery. We value fresh perspectives, encourage learning, and believe great attitudes and genuine curiosity matter more than prior experience.</p></div><div class="border-t pt-6"><p class="mb-2">To apply, email your resume and a brief note about yourself to: <a href="mailto:jobs@needstreet.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">jobs@needstreet.com</a></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> This role requires you to work from the office. Location – Technopark, Trivandrum.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="fullstack-developer" class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto"><div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8"><div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-user-cog h-8 w-8 text-slate-600" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 15H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><path d="m14.305 16.53.923-.382"></path><path d="m15.228 13.852-.923-.383"></path><path d="m16.852 12.228-.383-.923"></path><path d="m16.852 17.772-.383.924"></path><path d="m19.148 12.228.383-.923"></path><path d="m19.53 18.696-.382-.924"></path><path d="m20.772 13.852.924-.383"></path><path d="m20.772 16.148.924.383"></path><circle cx="18" cy="15" r="3"></circle><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg></div><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800">Full Stack Developer (React + Node.js)</h2></div><div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border"><div class="space-y-6 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed"><div><p class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-800 mb-4">Experience: 3+ years in full stack development</p></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">About ContinuousCare</h3><p>At ContinuousCare.io, we&#x27;re building the future of digital healthcare 
                    through a unified platform for virtual care, remote patient monitoring, 
                    care plans, and AI-powered engagement. Our platform supports doctors, 
                    clinics, hospitals, insurers, and patients across multiple regions—delivering 
                    continuous, accessible, and personalized healthcare experiences.</p><p class="mt-3">We are rapidly scaling our team and technology to meet the growing global demand for smart, preventive, and virtual-first care. If you are passionate about performance, scalability, and real-world impact—this role offers the opportunity to shape the future of healthcare tech alongside a cross-functional team.</p></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">Role Overview</h3><p>We&#x27;re looking for an experienced Full Stack Developer to join our team. In this 
                    role, you will build and maintain high-performance front-end interfaces and scalable 
                    backend APIs that power real-time, AI-enhanced, and healthcare-critical workflows.</p><p class="mt-3">This role requires strong expertise across both React and Node.js, comfort working with AI development tools, and a keen interest in building production-grade healthcare applications. Must be willing to work in hybrid mode.</p></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">What You&#x27;ll Bring</h3><h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Core Front-End Skills</h4><ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 mb-4"><li>Strong proficiency in JavaScript and HTML5</li><li>Expert knowledge of React.js and related tools:<ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-6 mt-1"><li>Hooks, Context API, component-based architecture</li><li>State management libraries (Redux, Zustand, etc.)</li></ul></li><li>Experience with Next.js and server-side rendering (SSR)</li><li>Styling expertise using Tailwind CSS, SASS, or styled-components</li><li>Ability to implement responsive UIs from Figma design specifications</li><li>Familiarity with Progressive Web Apps (PWA) including caching strategies and offline support</li><li>Working knowledge of WebRTC and real-time WebSocket-based interactions</li></ul><h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Core Back-End Skills</h4><ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 mb-4"><li>Advanced experience with Node.js and Express.js</li><li>Strong working knowledge of Sequelize ORM and MySQL for data modeling and performance tuning</li><li>Hands-on experience with ElasticSearch for advanced search capabilities</li><li>Proficiency with Redis and RabbitMQ and AWS SQS for caching and async queues</li><li>Experience building and optimizing REST APIs with proper security and rate-limiting</li><li>Experience with AWS services: EC2, RDS, S3, IAM, CloudWatch, Lambda, and SQS/SNS</li></ul><h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">AI-First Development Practices</h4><p class="mb-2">As part of an AI-native development team, you will regularly work with AI-powered features, APIs, and tools across the full stack.</p><ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 mb-4"><li>Experience integrating LLMs (OpenAI, Claude, etc.) and AI workflows</li><li>Understanding of prompt design, token management, and model orchestration</li><li>Familiarity with Model Context Protocols (MCPs) to enable dynamic AI behavior</li><li>Exposure to RAG pipelines and vector databases such as pgvector or Pinecone</li><li>Daily usage of AI dev tools like Cursor, Bolt.new, GitHub Copilot, or Codeium</li><li>Ability to implement AI-powered UIs like chat assistants, summarizers, and content generators</li><li>Bonus: Experience using AI tools for log analysis, test case generation, or observability</li></ul><h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Testing &amp; QA</h4><p class="mb-2">Strong experience in testing across the stack:</p><ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 mb-4"><li>Jest, Mocha, Supertest for backend</li><li>React Testing Library, Cypress, Playwright for frontend</li><li>Familiarity with tools like Postman, Newman, or API test automation</li><li>Understanding of writing maintainable, regression-proof code with CI-integrated testing workflows</li></ul></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">We would be interested to know about</h3><ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4"><li>Experience working on healthcare-related platforms i.e. familiarity with compliance requirements for HIPAA, GDPR and standard data protection regulations.</li><li>Awareness of healthcare data standards such as HL7 FHIR, ICD, LOINC etc.</li><li>Experience building for low-bandwidth environments or mobile-first markets</li><li>Contributions to open-source projects or communities around full stack development</li></ul></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">Why Join Us</h3><ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4"><li>Work on a mission-driven product transforming preventive and virtual healthcare</li><li>Be part of a team that embraces modern architecture and AI-first development practices</li><li>Build real-world solutions for doctors, patients, and healthcare institutions across the globe</li><li>Collaborate onsite with product, design, and engineering teams in our Trivandrum office</li><li>Take ownership of features that directly impact patient health and system efficiency</li></ul></div><div class="border-t pt-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">How to Apply</h3><p>Send your resume, GitHub/LinkedIn profile, and a short introduction to: <a href="mailto:jobs@needstreet.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">jobs@needstreet.com</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="subscriptions-management" class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto"><div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8"><div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-user-cog h-8 w-8 text-slate-600" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 15H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><path d="m14.305 16.53.923-.382"></path><path d="m15.228 13.852-.923-.383"></path><path d="m16.852 12.228-.383-.923"></path><path d="m16.852 17.772-.383.924"></path><path d="m19.148 12.228.383-.923"></path><path d="m19.53 18.696-.382-.924"></path><path d="m20.772 13.852.924-.383"></path><path d="m20.772 16.148.924.383"></path><circle cx="18" cy="15" r="3"></circle><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg></div><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800">Subscriptions Management Executive</h2></div><div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border"><div class="space-y-6 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6"><div><p class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-800"><strong>Location:</strong> Trivandrum</p></div><div><p class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-800"><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Full-Time</p></div></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">Position Overview</h3><p>We are looking for a <strong>detail-oriented and organized Subscriptions Management Executive</strong> to manage subscription plans, billing, and payment processes. The role involves monitoring subscriptions, ensuring timely collections, maintaining accurate records, and communicating effectively with customers. You will work with subscription management tools, payment platforms, and internal teams to deliver smooth and efficient operations.</p></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">Core Responsibilities</h3><ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 ml-4"><li>Monitor and manage subscriptions, pricing plans and other billable services.</li><li>Track all subscription related activities including sign-ups</li><li>Manage billing and payment-related communications through support channels</li><li>Coordinating with the relevant team to obtain necessary approvals where applicable.</li><li>Follow up with clients to ensure timely resolution.</li><li>Keep subscription and pricing information accurate and up to date across systems and public channels.</li><li>Prepare and present subscription and revenue reports, highlighting trends and risks.</li><li>Collaborate with internal teams, vendors, and payment partners to address issues.</li></ul></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">Requirements</h3><ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 ml-4"><li>Understanding of subscription-based business models and billing workflows.</li><li>Proficiency with subscription management tools</li><li>Familiarity with online payment gateways and basic regulatory guidelines.</li><li>Strong analytical, reporting, and problem-solving skills.</li><li>Excellent communication and customer-handling skills.</li></ul></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">Qualifications</h3><p>Bachelor&#x27;s degree in Business Administration, Finance, Commerce, or a related field.</p></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">Experience</h3><ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 ml-4"><li>At least 1 year experience in subscription management, billing, payments, or operations.</li><li>Prior experience in SaaS, e-commerce, or other subscription-based businesses is preferred.</li></ul></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">Why Join Us?</h3><ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 ml-4"><li>Be part of a fast-paced and growing business environment.</li><li>Gain exposure to global customers and modern subscription management platforms.</li><li>Opportunity to develop skills and grow within the organization.</li></ul></div><div class="border-t pt-6"><p>Send your resume to <a href="mailto:jobs@needstreet.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">jobs@needstreet.com</a> with the subject line: <strong>Subscriptions Management Executive – Application</strong>.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--><footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12"><div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-8"><div class="col-span-2 md:col-span-3 lg:col-span-2 mb-8 lg:mb-0"><div class="flex items-center mb-4"><a href="/ru"><img alt="ContinuousCare" loading="lazy" width="100" height="20" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="h-auto" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fcc-logo-white.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fcc-logo-white.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fcc-logo-white.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75"/></a></div><p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-6 max-w-md">Платформа цифрового здравоохранения для клиник и медицинских услуг